# Review gates for the coordination repo.
# A change is the human-in-the-loop handoff approval, enforced by GitHub branch protection
# (require review from Code Owners on the protected `main` branch).

# Contract changes are a cross-team commitment: BOTH teams must approve.
/contracts/        @acme/frontend-team @acme/backend-team

# Cross-team decisions: both teams sign off.
/decisions/        @acme/frontend-team @acme/backend-team

# Handoff messages + status transitions: both teams can see and approve.
# (The recipient acknowledging is a real human action recorded in PR review.)
/handoffs/         @acme/frontend-team @acme/backend-team

# Schema / CI / tooling: platform owners.
/handoffs/_schema/ @acme/platform-team
/.github/          @acme/platform-team
